# .chktexrc
# Suppress specific warnings for GTU Solution LaTeX files

# 9: `}` expected, found `)` (Triggered by "1)" enumeration)
# 10: Solo `)` found (Triggered by "1)" enumeration)
# 13: Intersentence spacing (`\@`) (Triggered by mnemonics)
# 17: Number of `(` doesn't match the number of `)` (Cumulative error of 9/10)
# 26: Remove spaces in front of punctuation (Triggered by code macros)
# 36: Space in front of parenthesis (Triggered by \code{method()})
# 44: User Regex (Triggered by \hline vs booktabs)

CmdLine
{
    -n 9
    -n 10
    -n 13
    -n 17
    -n 26
    -n 36
    -n 44
    -n 2
    -n 6
    -n 8
    -n 1
}
